            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Porphyrus <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>ertus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>urator</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>reg</abbr><ex>ionum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Fal</abbr><ex>ernae</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>Stat</abbr><ex>anae</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Aug(usti)</supplied> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex cert="low">ostri</ex></expan> Geni<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied> votum <lb n="5"/>solvit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Pagano; AE 1984: Porphyr[i]us. Diese Inschrift ist 1. Zeugnis für freigelassenen procurator regionis Falernae et Statanae; bezeugt, daß Teil des ager Falernus et Statanus in kaiserlichem Besitz ist. Die Inschrift ist nur durch Abschrift bekannt.</p>
            </div>
